{"word":"H1323 - בַּת - bath - bath - Apple","slug":"H1323","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">בַּת</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>bath"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>bath"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Apple"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D1;&#x05BC;&#x05EA; - bath</b> - <i>bath</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H1129\">H1129</a> (as feminine of <a href=\"#/H1121\">H1121</a>); a <i>daughter</i> (used in the same wide sense as other terms of relationship, literally and figuratively): - apple [of the eye], branch, company, daughter, X first, X old, + owl, town, village."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1121\">H1121</a>, <a href=\"#/H1122\">H1122</a>, <a href=\"#/H1125\">H1125</a>, <a href=\"#/H1126\">H1126</a>, <a href=\"#/H1127\">H1127</a>, <a href=\"#/H1128\">H1128</a>, <a href=\"#/H1130\">H1130</a>, <a href=\"#/H1132\">H1132</a>, <a href=\"#/H1133\">H1133</a>, <a href=\"#/H1134\">H1134</a>, <a href=\"#/H1135\">H1135</a>, <a href=\"#/H1136\">H1136</a>, <a href=\"#/H1139\">H1139</a>, <a href=\"#/H1142\">H1142</a>, <a href=\"#/H1144\">H1144</a>, <a href=\"#/H1145\">H1145</a>, <a href=\"#/H1148\">H1148</a>, <a href=\"#/H1151\">H1151</a>, <a href=\"#/H1332\">H1332</a>, <a href=\"#/H1337\">H1337</a>, <a href=\"#/H1339\">H1339</a>, <a href=\"#/H1340\">H1340</a>, <a href=\"#/H2618\">H2618</a>"}]}